A haunt from days gone by, I find it's charm gone. There is a variety of food and I've tried a few. Yet none being an enjoyment as its run of the mill. The tables are much better now and it's brighter. Yet it's not a place I would visit again. It's now a memory of a time past.

If its your first visit, you might find various interesting buys, the dough fritters a recommendation.
